channel.title: Do It [VIP] - ST3R30 [electronic]
channel.description:
So, if you have been listening to my music for long enough, you might remember [this ol' song, Do It](https://open.spotify.com/track/2s3bJwJIrYJqcc71D8399H?si=g1P55Hz7Qu-bX7I65-v76Q).
Well, I've gone and remade it now that, you know, I don't only have the free sounds anymore. Really happy with how it came out, give it a listen >[here](https://soundcloud.com/thatguywhousesauxy/do-it-vip)<.
Feedback is always welcomed.
